  <h2 id="guests-of-honor">Guests of Honor</h2>

  <p>We‚Äôre extremely excited to welcome our talented and distinguished guests of honor to CrossingsCon 2021! Read more about them <a href="/events/guests">here</a>.</p>

  <div class="container py-3">
  
  <div class="row guest-bio py-3 my-3 card">
    <div class="col col-12 col-md-4">
      <img src="/images/guests/diane-selfie.png" alt="A picture of Diane Duane" />
