    <div class="col col-12 col-md-8">
      <h5 class="mt-3 mt-md-0">Ursula Vernon</h5>
      <p>Ursula Vernon, author and illustrator, has written over fifteen books for children, several novels for adults, an <a href="https://diggercomic.com/">epic webcomic</a> called <em>Digger</em> and various short stories. She publishes children‚Äôs books under her own name and adult books under the pen name T. Kingfisher. She has received numerous awards, including the Hugo Award, the Nebula Award, and the Mythopoeic Fantasy Award for her work in various mediums. Having moved across the country several times, she eventually settled in Pittsboro, North Carolina, where she works full-time as an artist, writer, and creator of oddities.</p>

    </div>
