      <p>C.B. Lee is a Lambda Literary Award nominated writer of young adult science fiction and fantasy. Her works include the <em>Sidekick Squad series</em>, <em>Ben 10</em> graphic novels, <em>Out Now: Queer We Go Again</em>, <em>Minecraft: The Shipwreck</em>, <em>From A Certain Point Of View: The Empire Strikes Back</em>, and <em>A Clash of Steel: A Treasure Island Remix</em>. Lee‚Äôs work has been featured in Teen Vogue, Wired Magazine, Hypable, Tor‚Äôs Best of Fantasy and Sci Fi, and the American Library Association‚Äôs Rainbow List.</p>

